The '''Mud Puddle''' was a [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] on [[Ord Mantell/Legends|Ord Mantell]]. It was built in a former [[Speeder/Legends|speeder]] garage, and a murky puddle lay perpetually in front of its entrance. This forced patrons to get [[Water/Legends|wet]] when entering, and give rise to its name. The Mud Puddle catered mostly to locals, who regarded strangers with suspicion.

[[Arthen Brutt]] was one of these regulars, when he was sought out by the rogue [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] trainee [[Dal Konur]]. Shortly after, a team of operative hired by [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] to capture Konur also visited the cantina, gaining information on Konur's whereabouts from Brutt.

